    <p>While the meat was sizzling on the grill and Steffi prepared the rest of the food, I worked on fixing the tabletop of our camping table. It's a roll-up design held together by rubber bands. Unfortunately, they had completely worn out. Before leaving Hamburg, Steffi had been tasked with bringing us new rubber bands. So there I sat, threading the new bands through the holes.</p>
    <p>In the evening, while messing around a bit during dishwashing, we accidentally dropped one of our water bottles down a deep drain. That was a shame, but we had a good laugh about it. :)</p>
